description: I changed only the guitar tracks. I changed some timings in the riffs, added some quiet notes that were hard to hear, rewrote the solos and almost completely changed the outro. I made a lot of changes so it would be impossible to describe them in more detail. I am not sure in which key the guitar harmony is (I put it 7 half-tones lower). It probably isn't perfect, but I think it's much better than the last version.
title: Kindergarten
